Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.35,0:02:05.27,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}籠の中は安全で　绝对なのだと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.41,0:02:10.40,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}創造すら忘れた　その座に光は当たんないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.50,0:02:12.87,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}希望語る　不満散らす
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.97,0:02:14.76,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}革命の合図
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.03,0:02:18.28,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}誰にも追いつけないところまで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.42,0:02:25.31,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}突き抜け　修羅を越え　いつか
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.41,0:02:30.79,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}今にも圧倒的な支配が　僕の喉を乾かしたとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.97,0:02:35.39,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}奪わせないものは夢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.64,0:02:38.24,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}燃やせ　全神経の感覚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.51,0:02:42.98,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}誰に届けたいかすらもわからない音に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.08,0:02:48.16,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}意義は宿らない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.01,0:02:53.68,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}光を　もっと光を
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.78,0:02:57.72,OPJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}その頂へと
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,//------------------OPCN-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.35,0:02:05.27,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}牢笼里多么的安全　舒适而没有压力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.41,0:02:10.40,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}忘却了创造　这里将被光明抛弃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.50,0:02:12.87,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}来倾吐希望　让不满爆发
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.97,0:02:14.76,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}吹响革新的号角
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.03,0:02:18.28,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我要全力攀登　再不让他人企及
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.42,0:02:25.31,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}突破血雨腥风　让他们全都辟易
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.41,0:02:30.79,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}绝对的控制　将令我咽喉干渴无法言语
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.97,0:02:35.39,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}却无法夺去我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.64,0:02:38.24,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}让一切感官嘶吼激昂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.51,0:02:42.98,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}不把炽热的情感寄托在音符中唱响
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.08,0:02:48.16,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}怎会令心脏热血滚烫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.01,0:02:53.68,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}我需要光　更多的光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.78,0:02:57.72,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}向着顶点冲击
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.84,0:03:00.28,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Have an obsession for victory
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.51,0:03:02.90,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}I'm proud of myself and you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.06,0:03:05.78,OPCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}We must be the change we wish to see
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,//------------------EDJP-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.60,0:22:57.64,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fad(200,200)}青天響く霹靂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.05,0:23:01.00,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fad(200,200)}閃光眩むその間に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.66,0:23:08.18,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fad(200,200)}決して音を立てずに　じっと忍び寄る影
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.50,0:23:11.77,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fad(200,200)}騙し騙されて 失った
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.02,0:23:15.22,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fad(200,200)}罵り罵られて 奪った
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.56,0:23:19.25,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fad(200,200)}守りべき正義をすり減らして
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.52,0:23:22.61,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fad(200,200)}勝ち取るものなどない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.85,0:23:26.28,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fad(200,200)}籠の中から見上げた空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.59,0:23:29.85,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fad(200,200)}雨上がりの青の眩しさに
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.16,0:23:33.28,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fad(200,200)}囚われたままじゃ居られない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.43,0:23:36.77,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fad(200,200)}昔話なら捨てて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.92,0:23:40.33,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fad(200,200)}従うべきは他でもない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.66,0:23:44.00,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fad(200,200)}突き動かすほどの本能だ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.31,0:23:47.40,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fad(200,200)}ぼくはぼくじゃなきゃ居られない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.55,0:23:50.62,EDJP,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur8\fad(200,200)}変われるほど器用じゃないさ
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,//------------------EDCN-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.60,0:22:57.64,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}响彻青天的霹雳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.05,0:23:01.00,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}闪光掠过的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.66,0:23:08.18,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}无声无息　阴影迫近
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.50,0:23:11.77,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}尔虞我诈　逐渐失去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.02,0:23:15.22,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}以眼还眼　互相争夺
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.56,0:23:19.25,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}逐渐磨损本该保护的正以
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.52,0:23:22.61,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}也绝对不会赢得任何东西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.85,0:23:26.28,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}在笼中仰望到的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.59,0:23:29.85,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}雨过天晴眩目的蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.16,0:23:33.28,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}不甘永远被囚禁于此
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.43,0:23:36.77,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}哪怕要让我舍弃过去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.92,0:23:40.33,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}要遵从之物仅有一件
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.66,0:23:44.00,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}本能激发着无穷动力
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.31,0:23:47.40,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}无论如何都要做自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.55,0:23:50.62,EDCN,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur10\fad(200,200)}因为改变对我是难题
